trans-unit.source: Provides minimal design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Ger minimal designläge stöd för <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner class is identical to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner> class and provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner är identisk med den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner>klassen och har stöd för designtid för <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner>

trans-unit.source: It appears on the design surface as a plain gray box showing the name of the class and the ID of the specific <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Den visas i designvyn som en vanlig grå ruta som visar namnet på klassen och ID för specifikt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: You can change the rendering of a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control by overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method in the same manner as with any standard <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ändra renderingen av en anpassad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontroll genom att åsidosätta <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden på samma sätt som med alla standard <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property is overridden to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>egenskapen åsidosätts för att returnera alltid `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets an empty string (""), which indicates that the visual design environment should revert to default control rendering.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en tom sträng (""), vilket anger att visual designmiljön bör återgå till standardåtergivning för kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Binder designern till den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> control associated with the designer.
Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om designern ska använda en tillfällig kopia i stället för verkliga kontrollen som är associerade med designern för att generera designläge markering.
